                            List<Namespace> chemicalNamespaces,
                            BELSyntax form,

                            throws KamStoreException
Construct a new CustomDialect

Parameters:
kamInfo - KAMCatalogDao.KamInfo of the Kam the dialect is being constructed for
geneNamespaces - List of Namespaces to display NamespaceDomain.Gene values in. Items with a lower list index are assigned higher priority.
bpNamespaces - List of Namespaces to display NamespaceDomain.BiologicalProcess values in. Items with a lower list index are assigned higher priority.
chemicalNamespaces - List of Namespaces to display NamespaceDomain.Chemical values in. Items with a lower list index are assigned higher priority.
form - BELSyntax to use for label displays
removeNamespacePrefix - Should the Namespace prefix be removed from the node labels

Throws:
KamStoreException
